# readbro

Single MCP for file reads. **Never use built-in Read.**

| Tool | When |
|------|------|
| `read_file` / `read_files` | All file reads — LOD via `layer` (default L1) |
| `pack_context` | Multi-file bug/trace — `budget: 4000`, optional `target` |
| `blast_radius` | Before editing non-trivial source — call explicitly |

Full guide: `~/.agents/skills/readbro/SKILL.md`
